Sentencas: The oxygen tracer diffusion coefficient, D-b*, and the oxygen tracer surface exchange coefficient, k, were measured in Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3 - delta (BSCF5582) over the temperature range of 310-800 degrees C and the oxygen partial pressure range of 1.3 x 10(-3)-0.21 bar.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: Several measurement techniques were used: isotope exchange followed by depth profiling (IEDP) within individual single grains or line scanning (IELS) along the sample cross-section and gas-phase analysis (GPA).
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: Surface exchange kinetics was initially found to be slow and presumably inhibited by the formation of a passivating layer on the sample surface.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: High temperature pre-anneals (900-950 degrees C) changed the nature of this layer and enhanced surface exchange.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: Fast bulk oxygen diffusion and surface exchange kinetics were observed after high temperature pre-anneals within the temperature range studied.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The activation energies for O-18 tracer diffusion and surface exchange at 0.21 bar were 0.72 +/- 0.05 and 1.10 +/- 0.15 eV, respectively.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The tracer diffusion coefficient showed weak dependence upon oxygen partial pressure, whereas the surface exchange coefficient exhibited strong oxygen partial pressure dependence.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ

Sentencas: The microstructure of the samples (the porosity and grain size) had a profound effect on the measured tracer diffusion coefficient.
Titulo: Oxygen tracer diffusion and surface exchange kinetics in Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ
